					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This seems to record a gift of some land for repairs (?) to the temple of Irugīśvaram-uḍaiyār by Dēvāṇḍai and Irukkāṇḍai, the descendants of the founder of the temple, who is here called Kumbaḷagāmunḍa. Mention is made of Śelva-Gaṅgar during whose administration this gift was probably made.</p>						

						</summary>
